<% content_for(:title) { "Enlace expirado — Trato" } %>

<div class="min-h-screen bg-[#F8FAFC] flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-12">
  <div class="max-w-md w-full bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-8 md:p-10 text-center">
    <%# Expired icon %>
    <div class="mx-auto mb-6 h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-[#FEF3C7] flex items-center justify-center">
      <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#F59E0B]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m9-.75a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-9 3.75h.008v.008H12v-.008z" />
      </svg>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1E293B] mb-3 font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans']">
      Enlace expirado
    </h1>

    <p class="text-[#64748B] text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Este enlace para conectar tu Facebook ya no es válido.
      Los enlaces expiran después de 10 minutos por seguridad.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-[#F0FDF9] rounded-xl p-5 border border-[#0F766E]/10 mb-6">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 text-left">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#0F766E] mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.879 7.519c1.171-1.025 3.071-1.025 4.242 0 1.172 1.025 1.172 2.687 0 3.712-.203.179-.43.326-.67.442-.745.361-1.45.999-1.45 1.827v.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-9 5.25h.008v.008H12v-.008z" />
        </svg>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#0F766E] mb-1">¿Cómo obtener un nuevo enlace?</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#64748B] leading-relaxed">
            Escríbele a tu asistente por WhatsApp y pídele que te envíe
            un nuevo enlace para conectar tu Facebook.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="https://wa.me/<%= ENV.fetch('TRATO_WHATSAPP_NUMBER', '') %>"
       class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full px-6 py-3.5 bg-[#25D366] text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:opacity-90 transition-all active:scale-[0.98] shadow-lg shadow-[#25D366]/20"
       target="_blank"
       rel="noopener noreferrer">
      <svg class="w-5 h-5 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/>
      </svg>
      Escribir a mi asistente
    </a>

    <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-[#94A3B8]">
      Tu asistente te enviará un nuevo enlace en segundos.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
